.TH "snapshot_additional_pages" 9 "snapshot_additional_pages" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
snapshot_additional_pages \- Estimate the number of extra pages needed.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned int" snapshot_additional_pages
.BI "(struct zone *zone "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "zone" 12
Memory zone to carry out the computation for.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Estimate the number of additional pages needed for setting up a hibernation
image data structures for \fIzone\fP (usually, the returned value is greater than
the exact number).
